merb-interface
==============

HTML helper with dynamic CSS and JS.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Prerequisites:

merb-core, merb-slices, and merb-jquery

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Instructions for installation:

1.) Add merb-interface as a regular dependency - hostappname/config/init.rb

dependency 'merb-interface'

2.) Add merb-interface public directory - hostappname/config/rack.rb

use Merb::Rack::Static, MerbInterface.dir_for(:public)

3.) Add merb-interface routes - hostappname/config/router.rb

r.add_slice(:MerbInterface)

4.) Add merb-interface assets within the <head> - hostappname/app/views/layout/application.html.erb

<%= mi_assets %>

5.) Configure the slice (optional) - hostappname/config/init.rb

Merb::BootLoader.before_app_loads do
  
  Merb::Slices::config[:merb_interface] do |mi|
    mi[:button_color] = #000
    mi[:button_background_color] = #fff
  end
  
end

6.) Override the slice code (optional) - hostappname/

rake slices:merb-interface:install

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To see all available tasks for merb-interface run:

rake -T slices:merb-interface

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
